item.content:encoded:
Mac Icon Gallery was born because of the success of iosicongallery. It is inteded to showcase beautiful icon designs from the Mac App Store. The site was built and is maintained by Jim Nielsen.

Feedback or Icon Suggestions

Got an icon you think qualifies for this amazing gallery? Let me know about it. [contact-form-7 id="15" title="Contact form 1"]
